- In general I'm following modern material design with elements from Material 3 Expressive
- As this is a game scoring app it the design should be fun and have playful elements.
- The app is always in dark mode so you'll need to consider how to adapt designs to look best
- The app is for a game called Pooker which is a cross between Pool and Snooker
- adding animations is a great way to make the app more fun!
